name: FRIGHT IN HELL
description:
Fearfully? - gather your courage, smile 
and look fear straight in the eyes and it will recede. 
Fright is powerless in front of someone who laughs 
in his face and does not lower his gaze in front of him.

P.S. 
I confess: I love to eat meat. 
It walked, loved, looked.


best regards, Søuł.
